name: sample

prompt_map.0: Visualize a 3D papercut shadow box of an girl, where the art of paper cutting is taken to a new dimension. Layers of intricately cut paper are stacked and spaced within a box, creating a sense of depth and perspective. The girl is rendered in a series of silhouetted layers, each adding detail and contributing to a cohesive scene. Lighting plays a crucial role, casting shadows and highlighting the different layers, enhancing the three-dimensional effect. This style combines the precision of papercutting with the drama of shadow art, transforming the girl into a captivating visual narrative. The shadow box becomes a miniature stage, where the girl is the star of its own intricate, layered story.
